
For deploying the usr REFS app into a REFS environment:

* Shutdown the local REFS environment if it is already running.

* Setup sample app in the usr folder. 
    customerApp folder can be copied from LESDIR/samples/web/refs into the usr folder as a starting point for your custom app.

* From a command line where environment is bootstrapped, change directory into the customerApp folder.

* Run ant to deploy the app to the REFS folder (REFSDIR must be set).

* Run REFS database migration to load the custom app data

* Start the REFS environment.